{"timestamp":"2026-07-18T12:43:27.732Z","type":"event_msg","payload":{"type":"agent_message","message":"The product-side repair is now concrete and general, not benchmark keyed. On the frozen Zod checkout, `neighbors` improved from 1/7 callers to 7/7, now includes the abstract `_parse` target, removes the false `input` type construction, and resolves `isAsync` only to the authored `src` file instead of also returning the generated mirror. I’m running the full race/vet/build suite before checkpointing.","phase":"commentary","memory_citation":null}}
